title: Next Week: St Louis, Salt Lake City, Colorado Springs
description:
I wanted to specifically highlight a few cities and venues where I will be speaking about 12 Rules for Life (https://jordanbpeterson.com/12-rules-for-life/) from now until Oct 11. All venues listed at https://jordanbpeterson.com/events/

St Louis: https://bit.ly/2IyoMDu
Salt Lake City: https://bit.ly/2DLgitN
Colorado Springs: https://bit.ly/2Oqbuht

There may be a few tickets left for these lectures, as well: 

Des Moines, Oct 2: https://bit.ly/2OtN4nj
Kansas City, Oct 4: https://bit.ly/2QmNGZ8
Denver, Oct 7: https://bit.ly/2N241li
San Antonio, Oct 10: https://bit.ly/2txfHEr
Irving, Oct 11: https://bit.ly/2OtNA4J

These events have been a great pleasure. It is remarkable to see so many people trying to sort themselves out.
